Title: Ladies Rotary mother of pearl Havana bracelet watch LB02343/07
Description: chapelle_jewellery Visit our eBay Shop Add us to your Favourites list > Subscribe to our Newsletter > About Chapelle Delivery The Chapelle Guarantee Ladies Rotary mother of pearl Havana bracelet watch LB02343/07 RRP £179.00 Now £109.00 Description This ladies Rotary Havana watch has a classic design that combines a stainless steel bracelet with a round mother of pearl dial. The bracelet is secured by a push button clasp that blends neatly into the design of the bracelet. The stainless steel casing and bracelet feature polished and matte finishes which is a classic design combination. The round mother of pearl dial shimmers in gentle tones of pinks and creams and these colours are enhanced by the bright white crystals set in to the bezel. The crystal set bezel offers a touch of glamour and sparkle to this classic design. Silver coloured roman numerals and crystals mark the hours clearly and there is a date window at the three o’clock position. Each Rotary watch is sold in the official, branded Rotary presentation box and is supplied with a lifetime Rotary warranty. We are authorised stockists of ladies Rotary watches.
